TclMagick News
==============

2024-10-28
----------

* The Autotools configuration is modernized.

* TclMagick is updated to eliminate the libttkcommon "shim" library.

* TclMagick/TkMagick library names match the names produced by the TEA tcl.m4 module.

* Known crashes are rectified.

* Many bugs (mostly typos) are fixed.

* Test suite tests all pass.
